originalText.text:
I worked with Francisco Rojas and his service is outstanding!  He is very personable, friendly, and attentive.  He has years of experience and knows his stuff!  He listens to what you're looking for in a home and works his hardest to find what you're looking for holding your hand from beginning to end while educating you about the process the whole way through.

Finding a new home can be a stressful venture, especially in NYC so having an agent to eliminate the overwhelm is well worth it!  I highly recommend ZayMara Real Estate Group to anyone looking for  their new home!

Additionally, I discovered that they offer real estate investing courses so taking advantage of this is next on my list!

originalText.text: I signed up to take Francisco's online classes on Wholesaling .  They were incredibly informative and easy to understand.  As someone who is just now entering the real estate investment arena, Francisco made it very easy for me to grasp the basic concepts while also providing deeper insight on the various ways you can start and/or grow your business as a wholesaler/investor - and all for a much more reasonable price than many other real estate professionals are offering right now (trust me, I've done the research :-)).  Definitely a good investment of my time and money.  Highly recommend!
